.name
Trails
.author
Richie Bielak 
.description
Cute little program that leaves a trail behind the pointer when the mouse
is moved.  The trail has programmable symmetry, thickness, and length.  The
other interesting thing about this program is that it is written in
Modula-2 (source provided).  
